{"tid":852760,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"原來關愛座hunter為左抹黑保皇黨以外既對手 咩都做得出","createTime":"2018-10-08T05:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T17:08:02.000Z","uid":38523,"like":12,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a9cc3061df6aadf02aee0dae4f8156f3f88da35b","tid":852760,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T05:48:15.000Z","msg":"問佢特權調查沙中線<br />\n係唔係關鍵<br />\n佢死都唔肯答頂多兩隻字既答案<br />\n係 唔係<br />\n咁簡單都唔敢答<br />\n我依加就係度問<br />\n關愛座hunter可以入來答啦<br />\n大家等睇佢答一堆離題既野都唔敢答啦"},{"pid":"3b8e80be6ffc917a5600bc52c84a1aa62fef4e81","tid":852760,"uid":38523,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T05:49:40.000Z","msg":"第一問<br />\n特權條件調查沙中線<br />\n你認為係咪關鍵？<br />\n記住<br />\n答其他野係關鍵冇用<br />\n等關愛座入來答"},{"pid":"7c65087a394ed87769303b5caaf4789669cc8b7f","tid":852760,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T05:52:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43cb63d942000eb7c0256e6a4cc19f4672a426a8","tid":852760,"uid":79563,"like":33,"dislike":7,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"點睇都係你抹黑人啦"},{"pid":"09c8c1152b070d2b104fb48310621e16f10c9c04","tid":852760,"uid":40628,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T05:54:49.000Z","msg":"沙中線到而家連泛民都無咗聲氣，你想我哋點做去不如直接俾個意見"},{"pid":"6581de3e8dcccaf5ebcb6ceddfa6030e749a96c4","tid":852760,"uid":38523,"like":8,"dislike":12,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"43cb63d942000eb7c0256e6a4cc19f4672a426a8","tid":852760,"uid":79563,"like":33,"dislike":7,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"點睇都係你抹黑人啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T05:56:02.000Z","msg":"得啦<br />\n你呢種廢話可以收堆<br />\n第一我冇買中資<br />\n第二我冇去大陸收錢做野<br />\n講嫌疑我拍馬都追唔上關狗<br />\n不過你要扮睇唔到吹你唔漲<br />\n不過都係題外話<br />\n關狗可以入來答未"},{"pid":"5c74a204d229e51d19e89c1e4931bb75b8d11967","tid":852760,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T05:57:51.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n入來撐佢個班<br />\n可以鼓勵佢入來答架<br />\n呢條問題唔好難答