":"2018-10-08T06:15:03.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n先講明負評對我冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有種你就幫佢答<br />\n一係佢自己入來答<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3794d758e069ee6f5d8847adea791974d8fcb19c","tid":852760,"uid":206831,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T06:15:31.000Z","msg":"咪住<br />\n「特權調查沙中線係咪關鍵」<br />\n呢個問題本身就有bugs，個關鍵係乜呢？<br />\n<br />\n1.係解決沙中線現有問題？屌你啦擺明就禮崩樂壞，合理預期毫無成效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.係要揭露真相比公眾？<br />\n我話OK就OK.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再講，你憑咩assume一個有政治立場嘅人要全方位無死角地關心所有香港時事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要狙擊其他user OK啊，質疑埋政治立場都冇問題，但可唔可以理智啲，唔答一條問題完全代表唔到任何野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n甚至再退一步，曾經炒中資同埋喺某啲地方工作就代表今日唔能夠衷誠推動港獨咩？呢種概念擺明係支共嘅終生剝奪政治權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係呢個邏輯之下，任何宣傳建國嘅想法都應該消失啦下話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一日港豬 你成世都港豬 <br />\n你飲過閪茶 建國之後要清算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57a34056d196d9fa8df3da0a4d6f295a22958df","tid":852760,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T06:16:36.000Z","msg":"咩事<br />\n有冇原link睇返"},{"pid":"bc7ec2617f4c9f2dd41b2627b3333f714cc9f226","tid":852760,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3794d758e069ee6f5d8847adea791974d8fcb19c","tid":852760,"uid":206831,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T06:15:31.000Z","msg":"咪住<br />\n「特權調查沙中線係咪關鍵」<br />\n呢個問題本身就有bugs，個關鍵係乜呢？<br />\n<br />\n1.係解決沙中線現有問題？屌你啦擺明就禮崩樂壞，合理預期毫無成效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.係要揭露真相比公眾？<br />\n我話OK就OK.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再